				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey y'all.  Just getting back into the bard scene after a 2 year layoff to level up a cleric and a beastlord.  The bard was benched at 37.  After a week or so I'm up to 42 (holy cow I love swarm kiting!!!!).
<br />

<br />
Anywho, one thing I haven't done yet is LDoN as a bard.  I've noticed as a beastlord or cleric that a lot of times a bard will pull.  Well, I'm a bard now and wondering what makes me such a wonderful puller?  
<br />

<br />
So my question:  When you're the puller (as a bard) what songs are you using?  The followup question is:  At 42, do I have those songs?  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
Thanks for any replies!
<br />

<br />
--
<br />
Rachsolo - 42 Bardling of Rodcet Nife
<br />
&lt;Fizzle Fiends&gt;
