				<td colspan="2"><span>At 40 you got one of the best pulling songs you can possibly get -- Syvelian's Anti-Magic Aura.  It has 200 range - the best range possible on a bard song, it doesn't do damage which is good for those summoning mobs you will meet someday, and it knocks off those pesky damage shields or SoWs those mobs cast on each other.  If I was 42, I would be pulling every mob with Syvelian's and then slow/snaring them as they come into camp.</span></td>
